sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as 用户
    participant E as Editor
    participant W as WASM
    participant EN as Engine
    participant R as Renderer
    participant P as Preview

    Note over U,P: 编辑-渲染主流程

    U->>E: 输入图表代码
    E->>E: 防抖 300ms
    E->>W: validate(code)
    W->>EN: Engine.validate()
    EN-->>W: Diagnostic[]
    
    alt 语法错误
        W-->>E: 错误列表
        E->>E: 显示错误波浪线
        E->>P: 显示错误面板
    else 语法正确
        W-->>E: 验证通过
        E->>W: render(code, theme)
        W->>EN: Engine.render()
        EN-->>W: RenderHint
        
        alt FrontendJS (Mermaid)
            W-->>E: RenderHint::FrontendJS
            E->>R: mermaid.js.render()
            R-->>E: SVG String
        else ServerURL (PlantUML)
            W-->>E: RenderHint::ServerURL(url)
            E->>R: fetch(url)
            R-->>E: SVG/PNG
        end
        
        E->>P: 更新预览
        P-->>U: 显示图表
    end

